name: Dancing Queen
overview: Snatching trophies. Getting gorgeous. Turning it up. Alyssa Edwards rules the dance studio by day -- and the drag world by night.

episodes.name: Get to Werk!
episodes.overview: It's a new season at Beyond Belief Dance Company, and Justin's got big plans for the future. Alyssa goes all out to officiate a wedding.

episodes.name: Man, I Feel Like a Woman
episodes.overview: Justin's ready to buy his first home, but the purchase stirs up painful memories. A harsh critique in the studio leaves Kiana in tears.

episodes.name: Wrecking Ball
episodes.overview: With L.A. just a few days away, the Minis might not be ready to compete. Meanwhile, Justin makes plans to move and throws a blowout Halloween bash.

episodes.name: Alyssa's Secrets
episodes.overview: Justin gathers friends and family for an emotional reunion. "The Marcella Situation" comes to a head -- and there's only one solution.

episodes.name: Music Mishap
episodes.overview: Anjie and Kiana take a calculated risk, but will it pay off? A technical error puts Brooke's chances in jeopardy -- and Justin isn't happy.

episodes.name: Dragsgiving
episodes.overview: It's the first Thanksgiving in Justin's new home. Somebody pass the T! Back at the studio, the moms step in to get the Minis performance-ready.

episodes.name: Reigning Supreme
episodes.overview: Alyssa goes global with her first original song. The Teens and Minis travel to Arkansas to snatch trophies out of state.
